org.apache.flink.runtime.jobmanager.archive

Class MemoryArchivist

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.jobmanager.archive.MemoryArchivist
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArchiveListener

    public class MemoryArchivist
extends Object
implements ArchiveListener
    Implementation of the ArchiveListener, that archives old data of the JobManager in memory. This class must be thread safe, because it is accessed by the JobManager events and by the web server concurrently.
